{"recipe_desc": "An epic version of the Italian classic that is sure to please even the pickiest of eaters. If preparing for a crowd, the sauce can be made in advance and refrigerated for up to 2 days. Just reheat on the stovetop before assembling lasagna. Additionally, you can tightly wrap a fully assembled but unbaked lasagna with plastic wrap and keep it in the freezer for up to 2 months. To bake, just transfer it to the refrigerator for two days to defrost and bake as directed.", "recipe_category": ["Entrees"], "recipe_image": ["/recipes/better-lasagna/better-lasagna.jpg"], "recipe_total_time": ["PT1H30M"], "recipe_published_time": ["Jan 11, 2013"], "image_urls": ["http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/better-lasagna/better-lasagna.jpg"], "recipe_ingredients": ["1 tablespoon olive oil", "1 medium onion, chopped finely", "6 cloves garlic, minced", "\u00be pound ground beef", "\u00be pound sweet Italian sausage, cut in half length wise and chopped", "\u00bd teaspoon table salt", "\u00bd teaspoon ground black pepper", "&frac13; cup heavy cream", "28 ounce can tomato puree", "28 ounce can diced tomatoes, drained", "1 large egg", "15 ounces ricotta cheese (about 1 \u00be cups)", "1 cup grated Parmesan cheese", "\u00bd cup chopped fresh basil", "\u00bd teaspoon table salt", "\u00bd teaspoon ground black pepper", "16 ounces no-boil lasagna noodles", "16 ounces shredded mozzarella cheese", "reserved ricotta mixture", "reserved meat sauce", "\u00bc cup reserved meat sauce", "noodles, ricotta mixture, mozzarella cheese, meat sauce", "noodles, ricotta mixture, mozzarella cheese, meat sauce", "noodles, ricotta mixture, mozzarella cheese, meat sauce", "noodles, meat sauce", "remaining mozzarella cheese", "\u00bd cup grated Parmesan cheese", "cooking spray"], "recipe_prep_time": ["PT45M"], "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<title>Hearty Meat Lasagna Recipe - MakeBetterFood.com</title>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\